Title : Barry Sterling
Text : '''Barry Evan Sterling''' (November 11, 1943 &ndash; April 19, 2014) was an American businessman and politician.

From [[Memphis, Tennessee]], Sterling co-owned Sterling Company Realtors and was a probation officer in the juvenile court system. He served in the [[Tennessee House of Representatives]] as a [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]].<ref>[http://www.capitol.tn.gov/house/archives/92GA/Members/h83.htm Tennessee House of Representatives-92nd General Assembly-Barry E. Sterling]</ref><ref>[http://www.memorialparkfuneralandcemetery.com/obituaries/Barry-Sterling/#!/Obituary Barry Evan Sterling-obituary]</ref>

